Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.75,0:00:06.78,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.13,0:00:15.30,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.49,0:00:27.60,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.91,0:00:34.94,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Asta visited Nean, the town where \NRebecca and her siblings lived,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.94,0:00:39.91,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,but it turned out to be where Gauche's \Nbeloved little sister Marie lived, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.91,0:00:42.16,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Are you read—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.16,0:00:43.49,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.80,0:00:46.13,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Get away from her this instant, you trash!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.75,0:00:50.25,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,That night, a certain incident struck Nean.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.46,0:00:54.96,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Die, Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.44,0:00:59.81,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That's not even your house!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.58,0:01:05.34,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Snow? When did it pile up so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.34,0:01:06.81,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's not even the season for that yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.81,0:01:09.60,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What do you two think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.60,0:01:12.23,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,The kids are gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.32,0:01:20.95,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,Starting today,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.43,0:01:23.13,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,you're all my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.26,0:01:41.93,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Pursuit Over the Snow
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.50,0:03:00.65,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,Luca, Marco, where could \Nyou have gone at this hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.52,0:03:02.72,main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Basim!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.72,0:03:04.79,main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Helen, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.79,0:03:06.60,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Guess they didn't just go out to pee—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.60,0:03:07.72,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.83,0:03:11.77,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never let you marry my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.10,0:03:14.02,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Now's not the time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.39,0:03:17.08,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing more important \Nthan Marie, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.08,0:03:18.61,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.03,0:03:23.91,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what the heck's going on in this town?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.20,0:03:28.95,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it snowing this time \Nof year? This is absurd!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.27,0:03:31.60,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Noelle? What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.09,0:03:35.60,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I-I just happened to be in the area.\NIt's just a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.60,0:03:37.52,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,Who's this, Asta?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.52,0:03:39.29,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,She's one of my Magic Knight buddies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.29,0:03:41.46,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,And Noelle, this is my friend Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.46,0:03:42.59,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.59,0:03:43.72,italics,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,Buddy...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.13,0:03:45.40,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.40,0:03:46.32,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.32,0:03:47.85,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.65,0:03:50.10,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.17,0:03:54.65,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I saw a whole bunch of kids go \Nup to the mountains earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.65,0:03:55.60,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,What's that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.95,0:03:58.43,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Do you guys have some \Nfestival this late at night?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.43,0:03:59.86,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,That must be...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.31,0:04:03.11,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to make you bleed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.49,0:04:04.52,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.75,0:04:06.76,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Old hag...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.76,0:04:08.12,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,The old Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.65,0:04:11.49,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,I feel magical power in this snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.49,0:04:13.12,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,There is magic at work here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.53,0:04:15.62,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Magic that can control others...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.98,0:04:18.77,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,and that only affects children \Nwhose magic hasn't matured.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.77,0:04:19.88,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.40,0:04:23.26,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,A number of ours were taken, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.26,0:04:26.35,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,What do they mean to do, \Ntaking all these children?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.35,0:04:28.89,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, old hag, what do you mean, "taken"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.32,0:04:31.89,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me Marie was, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.47,0:04:34.61,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Sadly, that is what I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.61,0:04:35.72,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,You old hag!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.72,0:04:36.56,main,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,Sister Theresa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.56,0:04:39.68,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,How could you let that happen,\Nyou stupid old hag?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.68,0:04:40.86,main,Sister,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.26,0:04:45.47,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,So quick to resort to violence... \NYou really are a failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.47,0:04:47.16,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to hit me, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.16,0:04:51.47,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,But that won't bring back the children.\NIt won't bring back Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.77,0:04:54.41,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.19,0:04:58.52,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,But I won't feel better until I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.17,0:05:02.92,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,Asta! Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.92,0:05:05.42,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Asta, you bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.42,0:05:07.61,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on now, Gauche.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.61,0:05:09.83,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Just cool down a little, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.23,0:05:19.77,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,A Magic Knight needs to \Nstay calm at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.77,0:05:22.77,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Well, listen to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.81,0:05:26.21,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Calm, eh? You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.21,0:05:28.28,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So you finally understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.28,0:05:30.84,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I'll calmly kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.84,0:05:32.87,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I went too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.87,0:05:35.17,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,That hurt, you stupid little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.17,0:05:37.80,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait, wait! \NNow's not the time for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.80,0:05:40.11,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,We need to find some clues!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.11,0:05:42.49,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,What? As if it'll be that easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.36,0:05:48.00,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,The magic mirror that I have Marie \Nkeep with her at all times...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.67,0:05:51.75,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't be able to transmit \Nto it because of this snow,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.75,0:05:54.26,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,but if I search for the \Nmana in that mirror...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.26,0:05:56.40,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I should be able to figure out where she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.40,0:05:57.85,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.85,0:06:02.24,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I may have figured\Nthat out, but I'm still killing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.24,0:06:04.52,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you while giving thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.88,0:06:09.03,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going, as well. I'm going to get the \Nkids from the church and the town back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.92,0:06:12.75,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Old Sister, leave this to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.75,0:06:15.92,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,No. As much as it pains me to \Nsay it, this old hag will be useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.92,0:06:19.08,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? She's not just an ordinary old lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.28,0:06:23.25,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to lose to \Nyou young'uns just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.25,0:06:29.22,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,Asta... Marco's an idiot and Luca's too\Nheadstrong, so I'm worried about them...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.12,0:06:33.14,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do? If something \Nwere to happen to them...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.14,0:06:35.05,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Get a hold of yourself, Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.05,0:06:36.81,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.40,0:06:40.56,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine! I'll get them \Nback, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.67,0:06:45.84,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,They'll laugh at you if you're \Nall panicky when we get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.43,0:06:49.32,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.16,0:06:53.20,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.20,0:06:55.95,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I'm going, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.95,0:06:59.95,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,You can't fly on your own either, can you? \NDo you want to dangle, like him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.32,0:07:05.09,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,The town might be attacked again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.09,0:07:06.92,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Would you mind staying behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.35,0:07:10.20,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,And could you report back \Nto the Magic Knights?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.92,0:07:13.20,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you, Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.20,0:07:15.18,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I have to stay behind with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.37,0:07:34.63,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy I made so many friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.20,0:07:38.05,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,L-Let's all get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.57,0:07:51.80,italics,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.80,0:07:55.22,italics,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the church. What am I doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.37,0:07:59.22,italics,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone seems out of it. What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.19,0:08:02.00,italics,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.03,0:08:04.42,top,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you stay good boys and \Ngirls with the spell I'm using.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.42,0:08:07.45,italics,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Did he put a spell on everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.99,0:08:11.17,italics,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, Brother did say that
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.17,0:08:14.69,italics,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,the mirror he gave me would \Nprotect me from magic a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.69,0:08:16.74,flashback,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on to this mirror as if it were me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.05,0:08:18.60,italics,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.74,0:08:24.19,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like my spell on you has been broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.19,0:08:27.46,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why. You bad little girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.01,0:08:33.46,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,We can't be friends if you won't be \Na good girl and stay under my spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.37,0:08:38.63,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,But you're wrong. Putting someone under \Na spell and making them do what you say
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.63,0:08:41.26,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,doesn't make them a real friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.00,0:08:46.12,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,How could you say something so cruel?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.76,0:08:49.27,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,A friend would never say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.83,0:08:55.90,main,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,Neige...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.91,0:08:59.69,main,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to damage the goods.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.69,0:09:03.74,main,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, you're so hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.08,0:09:03.74,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Baro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.31,0:09:12.83,main,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,She's the prize this time. Imagine\Nhaving that much magic at her age!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.20,0:09:18.15,main,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,Having this many brats means a big payday!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.47,0:09:23.35,main,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,That brat barely has any magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.35,0:09:27.49,main,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to only bring ones \Nwith a lot of magic, Neige!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.49,0:09:28.89,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Baro.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.91,0:09:32.94,main,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,Just gonna have to throw \Ntrash like this away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.86,0:09:44.79,main,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh. Stop wasting my time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.89,0:09:50.25,main,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then... Let's draw the magic out of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.34,0:10:02.55,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,We're close. The mana's getting stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.55,0:10:04.14,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.14,0:10:09.43,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,These enemies must possess \Npowerful magic. Be on your guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.43,0:10:10.98,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me, Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.33,0:10:14.02,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Please be safe, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.68,0:10:29.96,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, please stay calm. \NWe, the Magic Knights, will find all the kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.76,0:10:32.25,main,Guy b,0000,0000,0000,,The Magic Knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.70,0:10:35.20,main,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,Please get my son back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.20,0:10:36.81,main,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.81,0:10:38.25,main,Pim,0000,0000,0000,,Where are Luca and Marco?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.25,0:10:39.38,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.92,0:10:43.51,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. Asta and Gauche \Nwill bring them all back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.51,0:10:46.19,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah! So don't you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.19,0:10:47.01,main,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.60,0:10:49.52,main,Kai,0000,0000,0000,,Why's our house broken?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.00,0:10:53.52,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stupidsta and Gauche will fix \Nthat when they get back, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.52,0:10:56.33,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,We should do what we can \Nto fix it up for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.33,0:10:58.73,main,Pim,0000,0000,0000,,There's snow everywhere inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.91,0:11:02.78,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I need to contact \Nthe other Magic Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.59,0:11:09.69,italics,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Knights' Headquarters here, bah-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.69,0:11:11.79,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't I seen you before?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.79,0:11:14.15,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you really from headquarters?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.15,0:11:21.21,italics,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha! It's not my main job, but \NCaptain Jack ordered me to help out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.21,0:11:26.01,italics,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,I've been doing so good lately that they're \Nletting me take a break from all the battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.01,0:11:27.84,italics,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Or something like that, bah-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.84,0:11:30.51,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care! We have an emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.51,0:11:32.81,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,There's snow! There's snow in Nean!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.81,0:11:34.81,italics,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Snow? How romantic!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.81,0:11:36.53,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.53,0:11:39.17,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Someone made this snow fall \Non the town using magic
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.17,0:11:41.96,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,so they could kidnap all the kids here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.96,0:11:44.82,italics,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,What? You should hurry up and \Ncontact the Magic Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.82,0:11:46.30,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I'm doing right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.62,0:11:49.15,italics,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.15,0:11:51.83,italics,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to worry \Nabout anymore! Bah-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.11,0:11:55.08,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow, I'm even more worried now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.16,0:12:06.01,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I sense mana in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.01,0:12:10.51,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,A cave. That must be where \Nall the abducted children are!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.07,0:12:13.48,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.12,0:12:16.48,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Gauche, could you let me down a sec?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.90,0:12:19.61,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Not my problem. I don't care \Nabout anyone besides Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.57,0:12:21.86,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to go, then jump off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.99,0:12:25.56,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hup!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.77,0:12:35.75,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Asta! How can you call \Nyourself a Magic Knight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.87,0:12:43.01,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care what happens to the others, \Nas long as I can protect Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.65,0:12:51.22,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,On the day that I, a former prisoner,\Njoined the Black Bulls, the captain told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.22,0:12:55.35,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You can just protect whoever \Nyou want to protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.40,0:12:58.36,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,And that's exactly what I'll be doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.00,0:13:00.99,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Marco!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.99,0:13:02.61,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.61,0:13:07.26,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,This is awful. He's covered in \Nwounds, and he's frostbitten.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.26,0:13:08.36,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Marco?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.92,0:13:12.73,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use. He's under a spell\Nand still unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.95,0:13:17.25,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,All right... Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.83,0:13:19.25,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,What are you—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.49,0:13:29.44,main,Marco,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Asta... Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.44,0:13:30.68,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Marco?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.08,0:13:34.41,italics,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,What was that just now? He erased the magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.91,0:13:37.44,main,Marco,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.44,0:13:38.55,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Just a second...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.23,0:13:43.01,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Flame Recovery Magic: Sacred Healing Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.57,0:13:48.03,main,Marco,0000,0000,0000,,It's so warm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.41,0:13:52.30,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing, old lady! \NYou can even heal wounds?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.30,0:13:54.48,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.48,0:13:56.54,main,Marco,0000,0000,0000,,I... don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.53,0:14:00.08,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,He's so hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.08,0:14:00.97,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Marco...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.51,0:14:05.07,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,We have to go save your \Nsister and the other kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.69,0:14:08.30,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Can you wait in that cave by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.30,0:14:11.96,main,Marco,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? No! I'm scared, Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.57,0:14:14.05,main,Marco,0000,0000,0000,,Stay with me, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.39,0:14:17.31,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about? \NYou're a man, too, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.27,0:14:21.19,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Just this once, I'll let you \Nborrow my Black Bulls robe!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.67,0:14:24.98,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you have this on, you'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.98,0:14:28.82,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's got Magic Knight \Ncourage in it, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.53,0:14:33.61,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You can wait until we get back, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.04,0:14:35.33,main,Marco,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.68,0:14:38.20,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,But don't forget! I'm only \Nletting you borrow it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.20,0:14:40.18,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to give it back to me later!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.18,0:14:42.33,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You'll give it back, right? \NAnd don't get any snot on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.64,0:14:43.88,main,Marco,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.43,0:14:48.01,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,All right, we have to hurry. \NI'm worried about the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.13,0:14:56.57,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a damn maze in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.57,0:14:59.35,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,But the mana's getting stronger and stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.35,0:15:02.60,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait a little longer, Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.17,0:15:13.11,main,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,Good, good. More, more!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.11,0:15:16.80,main,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to squeeze every last\Ndrop of magic out of you brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.91,0:15:20.11,main,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,And done.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.00,0:15:25.38,main,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then... Are we going \Nto use our prize next?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.76,0:15:31.12,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,N-No! S-Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.12,0:15:34.25,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.81,0:15:35.12,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,You can't defy Baro.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.12,0:15:42.93,main,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,Just give it up. I'm gonna make \Na fortune off of your magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.14,0:15:46.40,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Marie!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.53,0:15:50.03,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.51,0:15:52.28,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness! You're sa—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.04,0:15:59.03,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do to Marie, you bastards?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.37,0:16:07.11,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's an enemy, Baro! He has\Na Magic Knight robe on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.11,0:16:10.82,main,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! How'd they find us so quickly?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.82,0:16:14.07,main,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,Do something! Use your magic, Neige!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.07,0:16:15.30,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.30,0:16:18.30,main,Neight,0000,0000,0000,,Snow Magic: Snow Cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.76,0:16:21.39,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Mirror Magic: Mirror Shift.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.19,0:16:25.40,main,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the heck is that spell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.07,0:16:32.84,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can't hit him at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.07,0:16:35.20,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Marie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.20,0:16:38.62,main,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hurry up and use a \Ndifferent spell, you oaf!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.77,0:16:44.89,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,S-Snow Creation Magic: Snow Friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.83,0:16:52.37,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,Go, my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.67,0:17:01.20,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.93,0:17:06.51,main,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,Defeating one or two won't make a difference!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.51,0:17:10.82,main,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,Neige can keep creating an \Ninfinite number of these guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.82,0:17:11.69,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.65,0:17:16.15,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.65,0:17:18.16,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Mirror Magic:
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.91,0:17:20.86,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Reflect Refrain!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.08,0:17:27.66,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Time for a massacre.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.24,0:17:41.02,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,All of my friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.02,0:17:44.52,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,That guy's too strong. And he's scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.52,0:17:48.41,italics,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it... This isn't what we were told about.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.41,0:17:51.11,italics,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,I only accepted this job\Nbecause we were told that
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.11,0:17:53.44,italics,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,it'd just be draining brats of their magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.77,0:17:57.44,italics,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,What's the deal with this guy's magic?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.81,0:18:00.04,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do, Baro?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.04,0:18:02.01,main,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.01,0:18:06.95,italics,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Think! There has to be some way! Something...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.80,0:18:19.76,main,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,Move an inch, and see what happens to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.13,0:18:21.85,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.85,0:18:24.21,main,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that look?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.21,0:18:25.38,main,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.38,0:18:29.23,main,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,if I get annoyed and put a little \Ntoo much strength into my grip?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.69,0:18:35.48,main,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,Neige, beat him to a pulp—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.61,0:18:45.64,main,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.48,0:18:48.54,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Marie!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.71,0:19:05.06,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Everything's okay now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.06,0:19:06.91,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.91,0:19:08.56,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Marie?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.14,0:19:11.94,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.01,0:19:11.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.22,0:19:15.32,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard! How dare you \Nthrow something so dangerous?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.32,0:19:17.77,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,What if it had hit Marie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.77,0:19:20.67,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait, wait. This was to save Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.67,0:19:24.49,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, what if {\i1}you{\i0} had hit Marie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.49,0:19:26.87,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I'd ever hit her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.49,0:19:30.45,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,My love for Marie is too great.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.45,0:19:32.15,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.15,0:19:33.62,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.62,0:19:34.87,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away, Marie!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.87,0:19:35.91,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.11,0:19:40.84,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,These children have had their \Nmagic sucked out of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.93,0:19:46.85,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,If left like this, they may never \Nbe able to use magic again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.10,0:19:48.85,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Their magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.29,0:19:53.80,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,That man was saying how it'd \Nbe worth a lot of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.51,0:19:58.52,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,How could you do something so cruel?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.52,0:20:02.07,italics,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,Crap. This is not good. Not good at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.07,0:20:03.07,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,Baro?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.47,0:20:07.03,italics,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,We had enough on our hands \Nwith that monster of a guy,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.03,0:20:10.33,italics,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,but now that his friends have\Nshown up, we don't stand a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.08,0:20:13.85,italics,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,This boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.03,0:20:22.62,main,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck? He doesn't \Nhave any magic at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.62,0:20:26.25,main,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable! I've never \Nseen trash like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.25,0:20:28.47,main,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I take a closer look,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.47,0:20:31.60,main,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,you're just some peon that doesn't \Neven have a Magic Knight's robe!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.21,0:20:35.52,main,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,Neige, you take care of \Nthat sister complex freak.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.52,0:20:36.60,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.60,0:20:41.19,main,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll just have to take \Ncare of this peon myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.75,0:20:56.67,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I won't...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.36,0:20:59.93,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.05,0:22:35.56,sign_33083_276_Petit_Clover_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,520)}Pe{\c&H3BC020&}t{\c&HE2AF0F&}i{\c&H3BC020&}t C{\c&HE2AF0F&}l{\c&H3BC020&}o{\c&H0E42D4&}ve{\c&H3BC020&}r
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.17,0:22:34.81,main,Baro,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.06,0:22:39.02,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,1)}Staying Behind
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.35,0:22:37.75,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Staying Behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.01,0:22:43.31,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,Luca... Marco...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.92,0:22:47.59,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be okay. I'm sure Asta and the \Nothers will bring them back safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.44,0:22:53.57,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we do a quiz to lighten the mood?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.96,0:22:54.80,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.55,0:23:01.00,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,Then... Where is Asta from?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.21,0:23:03.83,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hage Village.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.83,0:23:05.17,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.17,0:23:06.59,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go next.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.96,0:23:08.55,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,How old is Asta?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.76,0:23:11.59,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,Fifteen, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.27,0:23:16.83,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,Then when is Asta's birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.83,0:23:18.67,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,October 4th.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.67,0:23:20.56,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,What is Asta's dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.56,0:23:25.56,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,Becoming the Wizard King someday... I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.56,0:23:27.57,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty knowledgeable.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.57,0:23:29.36,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,You, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.93,0:23:33.29,italics,Both,0000,0000,0000,,I really don't want to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.16,0:23:37.24,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, everyone, bah-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.83,0:23:40.83,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I can't hear you. Ready, and... bah-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.83,0:23:43.35,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, I get to be the star again!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.35,0:23:46.53,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Bah-ha Bah-ha-ho-ha{\i0}, Page 32:\N"Three-Leaf Sprouts."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.79,0:23:50.64,sign_34238_338_Page_2_The_Boys_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(234,1)}Page 32\N\N{\fs18} Three-Leaf Sprouts
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.53,0:23:48.96,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you the true bah-ha!
